name: The Hundreds x Hex Iphone 5 Case in Black Red
description:
PRE-ORDER, Coming in this week

The Hundreds Brand x Hex
IPhone 5 Case
Color: Black Red all over print
Limited Amounts

The The Hundreds X HEX Axis Wallet is crafted from coated canvas and features a custom made phone bed with camera hole, cash storage, three card slots, and a specially designed The Hundreds X HEX logo emblazoned on the right side of the case. Other highlights include a pivot hinge for optimized widescreen viewing and a protective front cover with elastic closure.
The Axis Wallet is available in three custom The Hundreds patterns  all-over Adam (full color), State (black and white), and Multi-camo  and is offered exclusively for the iPhone 5.

Grey canvas belt with lnavy buckle. Belt features embroidered Making Waves sailboats directly on canvas ribbing.
There is more to the sailboats in this making waves custom pattern if you look close. Take a close look at the sails on the ship and you will notice that they resemble our paper plane icon. We have been having a lot of fun hiding our icon into the designs for you to find!
Belts are strong, heavy duty and ready for whatever you throw at them.

description:
Nike Dunk Sb Diamond Supply Collab.
100% Authentic Nike SB Product
style code - 304292 402
colorway- aqua/chrome
year of release -2005
Size 10.5 and 13
DeadStock

The Tiffany Nike Dunks are perhaps the most hyped and sought after SBs ever. With only 4,000 pairs released, these sneakers sold out instantly.  These sneakers were a collaboration with skateboard apparel company Diamond Supply Co. and were designed after Tiffany & Co. jewelry boxes.  They feature a black alligator-like material on the uppers with a chrome swoosh.  Also, the aqua blue leather, isnt your normal leather.  Its very soft and is one of the best qualities you can find.

The Nike Dunk SB Low  Pro SB Cali is a limited edition shoe only released to quickstrike accounts in California. It features the state of California flags colors. This Nike Dunk SB is highly sought after by sneakerheads. It is rumored to have had only 444 produced.

name: Nike SB Dunk Hi Top Supreme Blues Size 10.5
description:
Nike SB DUnk Hi Top
100% Authentic Nike SB Product
100% Deadstock
Color: White/University Blue
Style: 307385-141
Release Date: August 2003

For their second collaboration with Nike, Supreme NYC decided to go with the high top dunk, three to be exact.  This version features white leather with light blue crocodile skin-like material.  The side panels contain gold stars making the shoe a little flashier and all three pairs come with a Supreme lace jewel.  There was rumored to be only 1,000 pairs of each sneaker released at the Supreme stores in New York and Tokyo.  People lined up days in advance to get these sneakers and theyve only gained more popularity and worth since.  The tongue on all three sneakers are cushioned.
